A directory of support programs for ircd.

respond         - utility for challenge-response authentication. (not built by
                  default; see respond/challenge.txt for details)
genssl.sh       - a small program used for generating a public and private
                  key pair
mkpasswd.c      - makes password for O lines
viconf.c        - edit your conf file without having to chdir su etc. etc.
                  also locks the file if file locking is used.
                  viconf is also installed with hard links as vimotd
                  to edit those files in a locked mode.
